description:
A slave today is not one who is bound by chains but one who is held captive in his brain. No matter your skin color, race, or ethnicity, you can connect with this poem because WE ALL have been enslaved by sin. But through Jesus we can rise up, break free, and experience the true freedom that’s found in Him!
